Preamble
--------

A media database program! Manages movies or books polymorphically!
Classes adhere to MVC. The user is presented a menu
to select a slew of operations (add, delete, view, search-view, exit).


Compilation Command
-------------------

Run the following command in the root directory of the files:

  make

Run the following command to clear the generated build and runtime files:

  make clean


Launching and Operating Instructions
------------------------------------

Launch program by entering

	./mdb


Adding a single or multiple items to the database is done by entering 1 from
the main menu, entering in how many items you would like to add, then entering
in the respective info for each item.

Delete a item that is in the database by entering 2 for "Delete a item", then
entering the full title of the item to delete.

Display all of the items currently in the database by entering 3 for "List all
items" from the main menu.

Exit the program by entering 0 for "Quit" at the main menu.


